column5: It's Joey and Paul's anniversary today and I forgot to send Paul a card!  You guys have a really good day. What's Paul making you for supper Hun? Or maybe he's taking you out somewhere? Which ever it is....wear the red.
Wow time flys.Happy day to you both. Yous are a great couple.
One year already......"Dang!"  I do have it on my calendar Roy but hell, I never check my calendar.....LOL  Congrats on year one Joey and Paul, my sincerest, much love to you both!

Thanks guys, time really does fly.  Can't believe its a year already.  We're having a great day here.  Paul got his new computer monitor and I got my camera lens I wanted.  Nice when you know what yer partner really wants  Looking forward to dinner this evening

HHMMMMMM Guess you learned how to use the camera then eh J? I do remember a conversation (which you probly never heard on the boat) with Paul,he wasnt going to buy it til you learned to use it.LOL   Nice gifts.
The course is Oct 6th, but I guess he couldn't wait
Happy Anniversary you guys!!! Geez Joey, from the looks of those pics, i dunno.....maybe you could show THEM a thing or three.  Have a great day guys  Paul
Time always flys when you're happy, enjoy the moment.
Here's to many more    Happy belated first Joey & Paul
Thanks everyone, we had a great year.  Looking forward to many, many more
